Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language): This paper deals with improving the quality of text-to-speech synthesis, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP) and speech processing. 
2. cs.SD (Sound): The paper focuses on improving the quality of synthesized speech, which is a sound signal. 
3. cs.SI (Speech and Audio Processing): The paper deals with improving the quality of speech synthesis, which is a subfield of speech and audio processing. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a new approach to improve the end-to-end TTS system, which involves the use of machine learning techniques. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to improve the quality of synthesized speech, which involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques.
